{Character_Name} has learned Special Move Critical Hit!
When you use Critical Hit, you can attack the target enemy with Kaishin's Ichigeki.
Special moves can only be used when her hit command appears during battle.

{Character_Name} has learned Special Move Saint's Poem!
Using the Saint's Poem will erase bad effects and restore HP for all allies! You can also bring back your dead friends!
He can only use his special move during battle when the command Hitsatsu appears.

{Character_Name} has learned Special Move Miracle Zone!
When you use Miracle Zone, The MP consumption of spells and special skills becomes zero. Sometimes he uses spells twice.
In addition, the damage from spells will increase while the effect is active!
Special moves can only be used when her hit command appears during battle.

{Character_Name} has learned the special move Ikkou!
You can use a shout to stagger all enemies.
Special moves can only be used when her hit command appears during battle.

{Character_Name} has learned Special Move Treasure Hunter!
If you damage your opponent as a treasure hunter, you will definitely get his treasure when you win the battle! The probability of dropping rare treasures is also greatly increased!
Plus, you can make the target enemy flinch!
Special moves can only be used when her hit command appears during battle.

{Character_Name} has learned Special Move Acrobat Star!
When you use Acrobat Star, all your allies' dodge rate and her counter occurrence rate will greatly increase!
He can only use his special move during battle when the command Hitsatsu appears.

{Character_Name} has learned Special Move Tension Boost!
When you use Tension Boost, your tension will rise all at once until you reach Super High Tension!
Special moves can only be used when her hit command appears during battle.

{Character_Name} has learned the special move Paladin Guard!
Using Paladin Guard does not increase the enemy's attack power. When he becomes angry, he collects all enemy attacks on himself. All attacks Disable it!
Special moves can only be used when her hit command appears during battle.

{Character_Name} has learned the special move Magic Roulette!
When you use Magic Roulette, your own MP will be recovered and sometimes the damage she deals to enemies will increase.
Special moves can only be used when her hit command appears during battle.

{Character_Name} has learned the special move: Fairies' Polka!
When you use the Fairies' Polka, the attack power and defense power of all allies will increase, and HP and MP will be continuously recovered!
Special moves can only be used when her hit command appears during battle.

{Character_Name} has learned Special Move God's Breath!
Using God's Breath will restore your MP. Sometimes he will use the spell twice.
He can only use his special move during battle when the command Hitsatsu appears.

{Character_Name} has learned Special Move Monster Zone!
Using the monster zone will increase your dodge probability and halve the damage you receive!
She also makes the enemy angry without increasing their attack power. Attracts the enemy's attention to herself. She makes the enemy who attacks her nervous!
Furthermore, even if you die in battle, you can definitely come back to life with the angel's protection!
He can only use his special move during battle when the command Hitsatsu appears.

{Character_Name} has learned Special Move Beast Mode!
When you use Beast Mode, you can act as fast as a beast over and over again. It also increases your attack and defense power!
Special moves can only be used when her hit command appears during battle.

{Character_Name} has learned Special Move Strengthening Gadget Type-0!
When you use the Strengthening Gadget Type 0, a magic circle will appear at your feet that increases the critical hit rate and damage of attacks and spells!
Special moves can only be used when her hit command appears during battle.

{Character_Name} has learned Special Move Kojin no Mai!
If you use the dance of the fierce god, you can raise the tension of all your allies to 2 levels.
Special moves can only be used when her hit command appears during battle.

{Character_Name} has learned the special move Palpunte!
When he uses Palpunte... He doesn't know what will happen! Just try using it!
He can only use his special move during battle when the command Hitsatsu appears.
